#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:1
msgid "E0034"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `implicit_use_builtin`"
msgstr "警告名称：`implicit_use_builtin`"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:5
msgid "Implicit use of definitions from `moonbitlang/core/builtin`."
msgstr "隐式使用了 `moonbitlang/core/builtin` 中的定义。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:7
msgid ""
"This warning is emitted when code implicitly relies on definitions from "
"`moonbitlang/core/builtin`. Consider importing the desired APIs "
"explicitly to make dependencies clearer."
msgstr ""
"当代码隐式依赖 `moonbitlang/core/builtin` 中的定义时，会发出此警告。建议显式导入\n"
"需要的 API，使依赖关系更清晰。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:11
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:13
msgid ""
"Here `Null` is inferred as the `Json::Null` constructor from "
"`moonbitlang/core/builtin` without an explicit type or qualification:"
msgstr ""
"这里的 `Null` 在没有显式类型或限定名的情况下，被推断为来自 "
"`moonbitlang/core/builtin` 的 `Json::Null` 构造器："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:16
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn check(value : Json) -> Int {\n"
"  fn classify(input) {\n"
"    match input {\n"
"      Null => 0\n"
"      _ => 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
"  classify(value)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:20
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "修改建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:22
msgid ""
"Make the builtin dependency explicit and qualify the constructor, or "
"otherwise add enough type information that the code no longer relies on "
"implicit builtin constructor inference."
msgstr ""
"请显式声明 builtin 依赖并限定构造器名称，或者加入足够的类型信息，使代码不再依"
"赖隐式的 builtin 构造器推断。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0034.md:26
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn check(value : Json) -> Int {\n"
"  fn classify(input : Json) {\n"
"    match input {\n"
"      Json::Null => 0\n"
"      _ => 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  }\n"
"\n"
"  classify(value)\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""
